nt|^z@3^b@2|fp|t|cs|1|at|
^-{  Opening the bidding with 1 of a suit  }
^-|fp||at|
Here's what we have learned so far about opening bids at the 1-level in our bidding system:

|cs|4|at|^-{A 1@H or 1@S opening bid promises ^*Iat least 5 cards^*N in the suit named.}

|cs|2|at|{A 1@C, 1@D, 1@H, or 1@S opening bid promises ^*Iat least 13^*N total points.}
^-
|
pg| ***** 261 ***** |


cs|3|at|Here are some examples of major suit opening bids (1@S or 1@H):

